		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">dXtr wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">isn't cc65 supported under Mac?</div>
<br />It's not "supported" as in the author provides tech support, but <a href="http://www.cc65.org/#Hosts" class="postlink">cc65.org</a> does state that Sheppy got it working on at least PowerPC-based Mac OS X with no changes from the FreeBSD configuration.

		

